{
  "stem": "11175.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were about 25 people, young ones, and also with a gruppenfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took us out to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every day, in the morning we got up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The soup consisted just of a little water with a-- a little potato, either sometimes a little black coffee.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every-- every day and evening, for-- [INAUDIBLE] they gave us a piece of bread, a half a pound of bread [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I smoked that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was a smoker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember, I take my portion from that bread, and I gave it away for somebody, he should give me a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A cigarette.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But this is not-- this is not the-- the-- the point of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The point is we had to go start it-- the daily routine from the work and what.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at night, there came to that barrack-- and if they touched somebody at that leg, because he was lame, they have to go out with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Every day, there is less.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took out a few people to be shot, to be shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I would-- then, when I found this out, that I was lame, every night I was laying so-- you know, together, when mine legs was almost with my mouth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They should not touch mine-- then, every day was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then, some women was also there, not in the same barrack, some other barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we heard the rumors in the morning that they got some women there, raped them, and they shot them, and-- they didn't went back to there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we were there in that-- I was there in that barrack-- well, almost for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We chopped wood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we brought-- and this-- this was consist of the-- that work, in chopping wood, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in the-- in the forest there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
